1012:src/main.cpp  ****         // Fourth-root curve (gamma=0.25) keeps each LED above its forward-voltage
1013:src/main.cpp  ****         // floor at the handoff points (50% raw ŌåÆ ~84% drive). Pressure adds a
1014:src/main.cpp  ****         // subtle ~75%ŌåÆ100% intensity scale.
